### **Example Input and Output**
#### **Input:**
| Trial | Trial Time | Pupil Size |
|-------|------------|------------|
| 1     | 0          | 4500       |
| 1     | 10         | 0          |
| 1     | 20         | 0          |
| 1     | 30         | 4800       |

#### **Output:**
| Trial | Trial Time | Pupil Size | Reconstructed Pupil Size |
|-------|------------|------------|--------------------------|
| 1     | 0          | 4500       | 4500                    |
| 1     | 10         | 0          | 4600                    |
| 1     | 20         | 0          | 4700                    |
| 1     | 30         | 4800       | 4800                    |
